WEBVTT

00:03.290 --> 00:03.995
<i>Previously on</i> Burden of Truth:

00:04.019 --> 00:05.274
I believe the girls suffer
from conversion disorder.

00:05.320 --> 00:07.002
You were supposed to
link the benzene to the

00:07.027 --> 00:08.744
girls' symptoms, not come
up with a new theory.

00:08.790 --> 00:11.830
<i>So Steve, someone you were
close with, committed suicide</i>

00:11.830 --> 00:15.200
and the tremors started
after that, right?

00:15.270 --> 00:18.730
- You're David Hanley's daughter?
- Yeah.

00:18.740 --> 00:20.900
[grunting]

00:20.970 --> 00:24.010
<i>Can you think of anyone
who might wanna do this?</i>

00:24.070 --> 00:25.670
<i>CTS, my old law firm.</i>

00:25.680 --> 00:29.180
It's over. Enjoy your cure.

00:36.090 --> 00:38.890
<i>How do you know
when a lawyer's lying?</i>

00:38.960 --> 00:42.290
Their lips are moving.
[laughter]

00:44.000 --> 00:50.074
